2006-02-07    <mihajlov@dyn-9-152-143-45.boeblingen.de.ibm.com>

	* gatherc.h, metric.h, reposd.c, rrepos.c:
	Bug 1426051: Changed data structure definitions to allow
	mixed 32 and 64 bit operations. Utilize the padding fields
	in 64 bit structures to identify them as 64 bit.
	The gatherd is always sending out data in native size (with
	integers in network order).

	* comms/mcdefs.h, comms/rcclt_ip.c, comms/rcserv_ip.c, 
	comms/rcstest.c:
	Bug 1426051: Fixed communication header encoding.

